    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480030/extras/9243e41a7c87abff4d0031b9897ccc3d.avif?t=1733484147\" width=608 height=266 /></span><br><u><strong>关于游戏</strong></u><br>A Way to be Dead 是一款非对称多人（最多 5 名玩家）游戏，由一名邪恶的医生追猎一群试图从被僵尸感染的医院逃跑的受害者。玩家可以在游戏中扮演莱利医生、受害者甚至僵尸，这款游戏设定存在于 Crania Games 开发的另一款主题游戏 Roots of Insanity 的游戏宇宙中。它为我们提供了从不同视角审视事件的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480030/extras/274818124d1fe6839ac15c14af43ec9d.poster.avif?t=1733484147\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480030/extras/274818124d1fe6839ac15c14af43ec9d.webm?t=1733484147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480030/extras/274818124d1fe6839ac15c14af43ec9d.mp4?t=1733484147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2></u><br>◆ 扮演僵尸、受害者和莱利医生<br>◆ 使用游戏胜利时获取的技能点使角色成长的能力<br>◆ 环境因素可使受害者发出很多噪音。受害者需要避开这些因素。而莱利博士需要使用相关的视觉和听觉线索追踪猎物！<br>◆ 选择多种路径在地图之间移动。受害者可使用地下隧道安全地前往各处并快速抵达关键地点。莱利医生可埋伏在这些关键地点周围。<br>◆ 帮助其他受害者一起逃跑，或变成僵尸永远留在奥古斯都瓦伦汀医院。<br>◆ 在比赛中个性定制所有变量。包括黑暗降临前时间、僵尸数量、战利品比例和莱利的突变限制。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480030/extras/77c83d843362e1ae2d756ba6a0891e7d.avif?t=1733484147\" width=606 height=118 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480030/extras/ac112298461501a5cba45900bed328cf.avif?t=1733484147\" width=610 height=267 /></span><br>Try 'Roots of Insanity' to find out story of Dr. Riley McClein.<br>",
